 "scr_litemuseb_slash_scr_litemuseb_gml_298_0": "\\E5* See^1? It's kind of like a snowflake^1! Hahaha!/",
 "scr_litemuseb_slash_scr_litemuseb_gml_299_0": "\\E6* \"Too many crumbs\"^1, your mother said./",
